column5: Spent last weekend up at the camp the Walleye were biting. Easy fishing good eating.....
dinner in the "man cave"... sweet.  Nice looking walleye you guys caught! wtg.
That picture of the feed looks like a good time...  Nice fish  Cheers  Craig
LOL, beauty dining room, for sure. There's ALWAYS something to be said for not havingf to set a table.... Looks like a great time, guys!
Nice man. I was up at Pointe au Baril last weekend too and we caught 50 Walleye in 2 days.  The fishing up there this time of year for those fish can't be beat.. unless your up in Sunset Country.

The smile says it all brother!! And the picture in the boathouse/garage captures perfectly what the weekend was all about. If you could bottle that and sell it you'd be a rich man. Thanks for posting! Jim
Real nice no mess no fuss, fry till golden brown a brown pop ah heaven.
THis report made me hungry.Oh that Garage needs a cleaning though
Thanks for the replies, the fish was hot, the beer was cold and the stories were, ah colorful ....good times indeed
wow good to hear you got into alot of fish!  Cheers!
